        <abstract> 
<p>Glad CD is pleased by his "Erasmus Darwin". Was not able to obtain book by Anna Seward [<hi rend="italic">Memoirs of the life of Dr Darwin</hi> (1804)]. Could CD check relevant passages for errors? Would be great honour if CD could arrange English translation. Wants to enlarge essay into book.</p> 
        </abstract>
